            Cancellation Policy for Monthly Plans:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Development/Growth plans:</strong> Cancellation requires 2
              months written notice. Both months must be fully paid.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Maintenance/Support plans:</strong> Cancellation requires 30
              days written notice
            </li>
            <li>
              Work completed during notice period remains property of Client
              upon full payment
            </li>
            <li>
              Monthly payments are <strong>non-refundable</strong> once the billing
              period has begun
            </li>
          </ul>

