            responsiveness. Estimated timelines will be provided in the project
            proposal and contract.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">
            5.1 Standard Delivery Timeframes
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-3"><strong>Monthly Project-Based Packages:</strong></p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Essential Package:</strong> 2 months (8-10 weeks total)
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Growth Package:</strong> 3 months (12-14 weeks total)
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Enterprise Package:</strong> 4 months (16-18 weeks total)
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4 mb-3"><strong>Individual Services:</strong></p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Landing Pages:</strong> 5-10 business days</li>
            <li>
              <strong>Small Business Websites (5-10 pages):</strong> 2-4 weeks
            </li>
            <li><strong>E-commerce Websites:</strong> 4-8 weeks</li>
            <li><strong>Custom Web Applications:</strong> 8-16 weeks</li>
            <li><strong>Logo Design:</strong> 5-7 business days</li>
            <li><strong>Brand Identity Package:</strong> 2-3 weeks</li>
            <li>
              <strong>SEO Strategy and Implementation:</strong> Ongoing, with initial
              setup in 2-3 weeks
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Video Production:</strong> 2-4 weeks depending on complexity
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Social Media Content (monthly package):</strong> Delivered
              weekly throughout the month
            </li>
          </ul>

