          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li>Client feedback and approval delays</li>
            <li>Changes in project scope or requirements</li>
            <li>Availability of third-party services or integrations</li>
            <li>Technical complexities discovered during development</li>
            <li>Content and materials provided by client</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            We commit to communicating any anticipated delays promptly and will
            work with you to adjust timelines accordingly.
          </p>
        </div>

